div1.p: United States of American - Western Distrcit of Washington, SS

I, A. Reeves Ayres, Clerk of the Cir- cuit Court for the Western District of Washington, do hereby certify that a bond in compilance with the within order has been filled and du- ly approved this 28th day of September, A.D. 1905.
Attest my hand and offical Seal this 29th day of September, A.D. 1905. A. Reeves Ayres, Clerk by Rm. H. Brikins. Deputy Clerk.
Pursuant to the within order and the above endorsement, I have this day released the within named defendant from custody as therein directed. C.B. Hopkinsm U.S. Marshal by AS Suvisson, Deputy.
